ergism', 'Caution is advised when brentuximab is used with potent CYP450 3A4 inhibitors (e.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/47211/', '[1] "Product Information. Xalkori (crizotinib)." Pfizer U.S. Pharmaceuticals Group, New York, NY.[2] Wohlt PD, Zheng L, Gunderson S, Balzar SA, Johnson BD, Fish JT "Recommendations for the use of medications with continuous enteral nutrition." Am J Health Syst Pharm 66 (2009): 1438-67[3] "Product Information. VFEND (voriconazole)." Pfizer U.S. Pharmaceuticals, New York, NY.', 'Paritaprevir, Cabotegravir, Zanamivir, Valaciclovir, Dolutegravir, Oseltamivir, Acyclovir, Brincidofovir, Elbasvir, Famciclovir, Doravirine, More', 'Pertuzumab, Cetuximab, Avelumab, Panitumumab, Obinutuzumab, Bevacizumab, Necitumumab, Dostarlimab, Ramucirumab, Atezolizumab, Amivantamab, More', 1767369485);
