e considered when brentuximab vedotin is used with other drugs that are also associated with these adverse effects.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/47216/', '[1] "Product Information. Adcetris (brentuximab vedotin)." Seattle Genetics Inc, Bothell, WA.[2] "Product Information. Accolate (zafirlukast)." Zeneca Pharmaceuticals, Wilmington, DE.', 'Amlodipine, Valsartan, Acetylsalicylic acid, Ezetimibe, Bempedoic acid, Indapamide, Gemfibrozil, Evinacumab, Evolocumab, Probucol, Dextrothyroxine, More', 'Pertuzumab, Cetuximab, Avelumab, Panitumumab, Obinutuzumab, Bevacizumab, Necitumumab, Dostarlimab, Ramucirumab, Atezolizumab, Amivantamab, More', 1767369485);
