 considered when brentuximab vedotin is used with other drugs that are also associated with these adverse effects.', 'Moderate', 'pharmacodynamic', NULL, 'https://ddinter2.scbdd.com/server/interact/47280/', '[1] "Product Information. Adcetris (brentuximab vedotin)." Seattle Genetics Inc, Bothell, WA.[2] "Product Information. Accolate (zafirlukast)." Zeneca Pharmaceuticals, Wilmington, DE.', 'Irinotecan', 'Pertuzumab, Cetuximab, Avelumab, Panitumumab, Obinutuzumab, Bevacizumab, Necitumumab, Dostarlimab, Ramucirumab, Atezolizumab, Amivantamab, More', 1767369485);
